Say 1 hour 20 mins reuse (with AAs to reduce wait possibly) and add a more wizardy name! <br />
<br />
Alternatively, 1 hour reuse and only 75% mana pres. And a more wizardy name!<br />
<br />
Other alternative is for it to be 36 min reuse, 100% mana pres and only last for 30 seconds.<br />
